EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0900Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   18 THRU 28 MAR WITHIN 20 MILES OF:
   A. 57-16N 008-05W.
   B. 57-30N 008-31W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON
   VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 282000Z MAR 14.
